---

<BaseLayout
  title="Uses | taka-techblog"
  description="普段の開発で使っているマシン・デスク環境・ガジェット・エディタ・AIツール・技術スタックの一覧。MacBook Pro M3・FlexiSpot電動昇降デスク・DXRacer・Dell 4Kモニター・AirPods Pro・Apple Watchなど実際に使っているものを紹介。"
>
  <div class="container uses-page">
    <header class="page-header animate-fade-in-up">
      <h1>Uses</h1>
      <p class="page-subtitle">普段の開発で使っているもの一覧</p>
    </header>

    <nav class="uses-toc animate-fade-in-up" aria-label="セクション一覧">
      {sections.map((section, i) => (
        <a href={`#sec-${i}`} class="toc-link">{section.title}</a>
      ))}
    </nav>

    <div class="uses-content">
      {sections.map((section, i) => (
        <section id={`sec-${i}`} class="uses-section animate-fade-in-up">
          <h2 class="section-title">{section.title}</h2>
          <ul class="item-list">
            {section.items.map((item) => (
              <li class="item">
                <p class="item-name">
                  {item.asin
                    ? <a href={`https://www.amazon.co.jp/dp/${item.asin}?tag=${associateId}`} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer sponsored" class="item-link">{item.name}</a>
                    : item.name
                  }
                </p>
                <p class="item-desc">{item.description}</p>
                {item.asin && (
                  <a
                    href={`https://www.amazon.co.jp/dp/${item.asin}?tag=${associateId}`}
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noopener noreferrer sponsored"
                    class="amazon-btn"
                  >
                    <span class="amazon-pr">PR</span>
                    Amazonで見る →
                  </a>
                )}
              </li>
            ))}
          </ul>
        </section>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .uses-page {
    padding-top: 3rem;
    padding-bottom: 5rem;
  }

  .page-header {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .page-header h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .page-subtitle {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  .uses-toc {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    max-width: 720px;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    padding-bottom: 2rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .toc-link {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: 0.35em 0.8em;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    background: var(--color-surface);
    transition: color 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
  }

  .toc-link:hover {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    border-color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .uses-content {
    display: grid;
    gap: 3rem;
    max-width: 720px;
  }

  .uses-section {
    scroll-margin-top: calc(var(--header-height) + 1rem);
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    color: var(--color-accent);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .item-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    display: grid;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .item-name {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .item-desc {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
